      "id": "214323674849146",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Best game Ive played",
      "review_description": "As a content creator, I love to create videos on this game. The community is so friendly, the devs are helpful and overall the game is great. I really recommend getting this game.\n\nThe game is really addictive and the community is so friendly, I was in beta access for this game and even though the community was small there was still so much activity. I would highly recommend the game and even have a few games at the least. \n\nThe developers and higher ranks in the discord server are so friendly and they listen and add your suggestions with no hesitation. The game is exactly like splatoon but for VR and probably a great kids version of vr shooter games for family friendly people. \n\nOverall, please get the game, you are very warmly welcome to the nano force community. I can’t wait to see you there :)",
